HISTORY "CHANNEL HISTORY" "CHAT HISTORY"

You can see chat history for various channels with the following commands:
  SAYHISTORY - say, oocsay, gsay, emote, socials
  TELLHISTORY - tells and replies
  EHISTORY - etalk
  /HISTORY <channel> - slash-channels

